                    <p class='text-justify leading-relaxed'>
                        Abbas is software developer who is passionate about building web applications and solving
                        problems. He is currently working at FPT Software Malaysia.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section class='w-full text-white mt-8'>
                    <h1 class='underline underline-offset-4 font-medium text-lg'>Work</h1>
                    <p class='text-justify leading-relaxed'>
                        Abbas is software developer who is passionate about building web applications and solving
                        problems. He is currently working at FPT Software Malaysia.
                    </p>
                </section>
            </main>
        </Default>
    </body>
</html>
